    <div class='main'>
        <h1 class="title">笔记-Ubuntu美化</h1>
        <div class="stuff">
            <span>二月 25, 2020</span>
            
  <ul class="post-tags-list" itemprop="keywords"><li class="post-tags-list-item"><a class="post-tags-list-link" href="/tags/Ubuntu/" rel="tag">Ubuntu</a></li></ul>


        </div>
        <div class="content markdown">
            <p><strong>笔记小记：该篇笔记记录了个人在换成Ubuntu18.04系统后，对系统的美化过程</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>安装gnome-tweak-tool  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apt install gnome-tweak-tool</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>安装gnome-shell-extensions  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apt install gnome-shell-extensions</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>安装gnome-shell-extension-dashtodock  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apt install gnome-shell-extension-dashtodock</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
安装完以上3个软件后，重启下电脑</li>
</ul>
<ol>
<li>找到安装好的“<code>优化</code>”软件，点“<code>扩展</code>”，打开“<code>User themes</code>”插件，在“<code>优化</code>”首页，选择主题、图标和shell的样式。  <table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mrgaodi/CDN/img/ubuntu-beautify-001.png"></th>
<th align="center"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mrgaodi/CDN/img/ubuntu-beautify-002.png"></th>
</tr>
</thead>
</table>
</li>
<li>在“<code>扩展</code>”中找到“<code>Dash to dock</code>”，点“<code>⚙</code>”，取消“<code>面板模式：延伸到屏幕边缘</code>”的勾选。———<em>注意：不要打开该扩展，不然会出现两个dock。</em><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mrgaodi/CDN/img/ubuntu-beautify-003.png"></th>
<th align="center"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mrgaodi/CDN/img/ubuntu-beautify-004.png"></th>
</tr>
</thead>
</table>
</li>
<li>下载桌面主题和图标<br>gnome主题下载网址：<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://www.gnome-look.org/">https://www.gnome-look.org/</a><br>我使用的主题和图标：<br>桌面主题是：<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://www.pling.com/s/Gnome/p/1275087/">McMojave</a><br>图标主题：<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://www.pling.com/s/Gnome/p/1166289/">Papirus</a><br>shell主题：McMojave 自带的shell主题  </li>
<li>美化结果：<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mrgaodi/CDN/img/ubuntu-beautify-005.png"></th>
<th align="center"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mrgaodi/CDN/img/ubuntu-beautify-006.png"></th>
</tr>
</thead>
</table>
</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>终端<br>打开本地的终端配置文件<code>~/.bashrc</code>，按以下内容修改<figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> [ <span class="string">&quot;$color_prompt&quot;</span> = yes ]; then</span><br><span class="line">    # PS1=<span class="string">&#x27;$&#123;debian_chroot:+($debian_chroot)&#125;\[\033[01;32m\]\u@\h\[\033[00m\]:\[\033[01;34m\]\w\[\033[00m\]\$ &#x27;</span> 原本的配置</span><br><span class="line">    PS1=<span class="string">&#x27;$&#123;debian_chroot:+($debian_chroot)&#125;\[\033[01;36m\]&gt;\[\033[00m\] \[\033[01;34m\]\W\[\033[00m\] \[\033[01;32m\]\$\[\033[00m\] &#x27;</span> 修改之后的配置</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">    # PS1=<span class="string">&#x27;$&#123;debian_chroot:+($debian_chroot)&#125;\u@\h:\w\$ &#x27;</span> 原来的配置</span><br><span class="line">    PS1=<span class="string">&#x27;$&#123;debian_chroot:+($debian_chroot)&#125;&gt; \W \$ &#x27;</span> 修改之后的配置</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
[\033[01;34m]：字符颜色<br>\W：终端上只显示当前文件夹的名字<br>\w：显示全部文件路径<br>\h：机器名<br>\u：用户名  </li>
<li>修改登陆界面的背景<br>选择一张喜欢的图片放到<code>/usr/share/backgrounds/</code>目录下。<br>打开<code>/etc/alternatives/gdm3.css</code>，找到<code>lockDialogGroup</code>对其进行修改。</li>
</ul>
<pre><code class="vim">#lockDialogGroup &#123;
    /* background: #2c001e url(resource:///org/gnome/shell/theme/noise-texture.png); */
    background: #2c001e url(file:///usr/share/backgrounds/xxx.jpg);  /*你选择的图片的路径*/
    background-repeat: no-repeat; /* repeat */
    background-size: cover; /*新增*/
    background-position: center; /*新增*/
    &#125;
</code></pre>
<p>重启电脑，再次打开时你就会发现登陆界面的背景已经变成了你选择的图片了。</p>

            <!--[if lt IE 9]><script>document.createElement('audio');</script><![endif]-->
